data.description: Welcome to your dream investment property in the heart of North Miami! Newly renovated gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a pool that makes it an ideal haven for Airbnb investors. The open kitchen concept creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests. Step outside to discover the outdoor kitchen area, a haven for al fresco dining and entertaining. The property also features a convenient outdoor shower, adding a touch of luxury and functionality. Surrounded by shopping centers, offering residents easy access to amenities and services. Whether you're looking for a lucrative investment or a stylish place to call home, this property ticks all the boxes. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of North Miami paradise schedule you’re showing today.
